day - Variable in class es.us.alumn.miggoncan2.model.entities.ShiftCycle
All three field ShiftCycle.day, ShiftCycle.month and ShiftCycle.year are used to identify from which day the cycle-shifts should be calculated For example, if we had started on Frebuary of 2020 with the following cycle: 1/2/2020: Sebastian and Diana 2/2/2020: Alex and Rasim 3/2/2020: Irati and Laura Then, the reference of the cycle-shift "Sebastian and Diana" would be: day=1 month=2 year=2020

DayConfiguration - Class in es.us.alumn.miggoncan2.model.entities
This Entity represents a specific conditions to take into account when creating the schedule for a certain day of a Calendar Moreover, a DayConfiguration can be used to express one-time additions to the current ShiftConfiguration.
